This is the notes for ArtDirection 

there are going to be times we are going to want to show 
cropped or zoomed in parts of an image for certian screen sizes 

this is what we call art direction 

##Art direction 
we are going to attempt this files we have 

to implement art direction we are going to use the picture element 
last time we used this element we use the source element with the 
type attribute 

this time we are going to use the media attribute 
we are going to write a media condition for the max width of 500px for mobile 

so when we resize the page we will see the difference 